{"tid":2143594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好感動 林鄭今公佈詳情 手足終於成功爭取到香港全民普選篩","createTime":"2020-08-07T07:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T08:38:47.000Z","uid":150912,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d51c1f4782c5fedeb8401f464b4a90132a23d0be","tid":2143594,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:41:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200807/1779417.htm?from=fb_et_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200807%2F1779417.htm%3Ffrom%3Dfb_et_news&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=b3894b08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200807/1779417.htm?from=fb_et_news</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥下午3點將宣布「香港全民普篩」　最快兩周後實施<br />\n     <br />\n<br />\n記者鄭思楠／綜合報導<br />\n香港新冠肺炎疫情再度爆發，確診病例數不斷上升。近日社會上有聲音要求，政府應為全港市民免費進行病毒檢測。港媒報導，特首林鄭月娥將於今日（7日）下午3時親自召開記者會，宣佈一次性免費為全港市民進行自願性病毒檢測。<br />\n綜合港媒報導，港府下午1時半發稿，特首林鄭月娥將於今日下午3時在香港添馬添美道二號政府總部地下演講廳舉行記者會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足在天安靈"},{"pid":"f0022065b833924b4e548183868ac85839ffcda9","tid":2143594,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"感動香港"},{"pid":"93d54ad339fef3d1651f38a9504fd46593ddae85","tid":2143594,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:45:18.000Z","msg":"死左咁多手足<br />\n都係為左依下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678d4e18d16adbaeafbbfb90efdbff276324a604","tid":2143594,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:49:58.000Z","msg":"進行自願 性病毒 檢測"},{"pid":"fdd85c16521afae88714c395c78de0a7c419f82f","tid":2143594,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:50:39.000Z","msg":"block"},{"pid":"ca4c6502676ee1403d0a719528ab6f029b86f58a","tid":2143594,"uid":268271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"